rows.label: qst201609_msg0001
rows.name:
Now then, finally big night arrive!
Friend Nanakoori, ready for concert?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0003
rows.name: Nanakoori?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0004
rows.name:
Friendokay?
Have tummyache?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0005
rows.name:
...Mmm, no, my stomach is fine...
... But I don't know if I can do it.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0006
rows.name:
It would appear that she has trouble
coping with the excessive stress.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0007
rows.name:
But that terrible!
Concert have to be canceled?!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0008
rows.name:
It'sokay, there's still time before the gig.
We can use it to get Nanakoori to relax.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0009
rows.name:
Trick of Tora when stressed is
to eat favorite food until calm.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0010
rows.name: Nanakoori have some Tasty Sausage too?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0011
rows.name: I think she'd just get heartburn...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0012
rows.name:
On the other hand, having a snack
would form a distraction. It may not be
such a bad idea, after all...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0013
rows.name:
Right! So we'll try to feed Nanakoori
her favorite food to get her a bit
more relaxed.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0014
rows.name:
Friend Nanakoori, what is favorite thing?
Teetapz bring, right away!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0015
rows.name: Excuse me? That's awfully sudden...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0016
rows.name:
Ah, no, we were wondering what your
favorite food is. Don't think too much,
just say whatever comes to mind.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0017
rows.name:
Ah,okay, mmm...
I saw some Champ's Churros out
front, I wouldn't mind trying those...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0018
rows.name:
Let's say, ten of them?
So Beary can try them, too...?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0019
rows.name:
Beary eat more than fair share...
But no time for grumble! We buy
and come back!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0020
rows.name:
And until friends return, Teetapz keep
waiting audience entertained with gift
of gab!
